{"tid":729770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係中時] 紐時：中國製造2025終會成功","createTime":"2018-07-05T00:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T12:12:45.000Z","uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e7605f246a96eedb27202d889d7966d4b628d4fe","tid":729770,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T00:08:54.000Z","msg":"紐時：中國製造2025終會成功<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20180705000579-260102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Fnewspapers%2F20180705000579-260102&d=E4v4%2B%2BvUR8WhfjwABT4B4wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=55f5de2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20180705000579-260102</a><br />\n<br />\n儘管美國總統川普掀起貿易戰意圖阻止，大陸仍將成功打造出能與美國匹敵的強大科技產業。原因是早在北京啟動「中國製造2025」之前，面臨金融海嘯、國內工資上漲等趨勢衝擊的公司與地方政府，就已跨出工業現代化和自動化的步伐。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">《紐約時報》駐香港科技專欄作家李媛（音譯）</span>表示，根據廣東省東莞市銘普光磁股份有限公司的員工描述，這裡曾經雇用大量工人，4樓廠房是一片「人山人海」，但現在這裡滿是一排排呼呼作響的機械，原本需要15個人經過26道程序才能完成的作業，現在靠機械臂就行了。<br />\n<br />\n這家工廠的現狀顯示，「中國製造2025」，這項旨在壯大國家製造業，在自動化、晶片與自駕車等先進產業領先外國的遠大計畫，並不是僅僅是由大陸領導階層由上而下在推動，同時也受到激烈的市場競爭而驅動。<br />\n<br />\n像銘普光磁這樣的企業就是因市場而率先自動化。他們知道工業若不革新，就會凋零。除了銘普光磁，蘇州、溫州、徐州及上海周圍其他工業地區也提出自己的自動化計畫。<br />\n<br />\n廣東省智能機器人研究院院長張國軍表示，「『中國製造2025』是一輛汽車，它的引擎已經啟動並且正在前進」。該機構是數個由地方政府支持，協助工廠升級的研究中心之一。東莞市早在國家計畫提出之前，就已經展開自動化，國家政策則是給民間一個具體方向。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紐約時報因此認為，大陸工業現代化可能無法如期在2025年完成，也許還要再晚好幾年。但大陸將會達成目標，因為現實要求這麼做。</span><br />\n<br />\n(中國時報)"},{"pid":"8bc1665f2d6caa3e453ca94fed06b0cbad0dfa57","tid":729770,"uid":57376,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T00:09:30.000Z","msg":"又話唔好再提嘅！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06831a46fc17cfc08ab189620b9acdbe8a8be77a","tid":729770,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T00:10:32.000Z","msg":"繼續吹"},{"pid":"0bc39cc53056336a6a500b61125e7fda0dea9761","tid":729770,"uid":52942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T00:12:00.000Z","msg":"再吹大d最好比侵侵知， 打多兩棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88eeea04f57e468aea0d4429066b036f9f6dfca8","tid":729770,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T00:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7319d2f103395aa82c9bea9fc005f03b5b5d6a0","tid":729770,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:31:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">為什麼美國無法阻止「中國製造2025」走向成功</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20180705/made-in-china-2025-dongguan/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Ftechnology%2F20180705%2Fmade-in-china-2025-dongguan%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=E4v4%2B%2BvUR8WhfjwABT4B4wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=4aaff5c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20180705/made-in-china-2025-dongguan/zh-hant/</a>"},{"pid":"9ff16e503e63deb0f924eae94e5bcbda36649d08","tid":729770,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3b9fbb08f80835e04e64413efb24b4788253aa","tid":729770,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"仲話做報紙，收風咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28886804afa7d2bee339f193c0e51fa5db2594b5","tid":729770,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkg